{"id":"fc300e2f-f3f7-4a16-8ce8-c7898130b173","name":"Taishiro Toyomitsu (Cop au)","description":"<p><strong>Taishiro Toyomitsu</strong><span> (豊とよ満みつ太たい志し郎ろう <em>Toyomitsu Taishirō</em></span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 238)\"><strong>?</strong></span></a><span>)</span>,<a href=\"https://myheroacademia.fandom.com/wiki/Taishiro_Toyomitsu#cite_note-auto-b5b991ebf55ae0e9431a7a17368ea648-2\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">[2]</a> also known as <strong>BMI Hero: Fat Gum</strong><span> (BMIビーエムアイヒーロー ファットガム <em>Bīemuai Hīrō Fatto Gamu</em></span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 238)\"><strong>?</strong></span></a><span>)</span>, is the current <a href=\"https://myheroacademia.fandom.com/wiki/Hero_Billboard_Chart_JP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">No. 58</a> <a href=\"https://myheroacademia.fandom.com/wiki/Heroes\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Pro Hero</a>.<a href=\"https://myheroacademia.fandom.com/wiki/Taishiro_Toyomitsu#cite_note-auto-51dd166a329a9fdf44fc5b4a207484f3-3\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">[3]</a></p><p>He employed <a href=\"https://myheroacademia.fandom.com/wiki/Tamaki_Amajiki\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Suneater</a> and <a href=\"https://myheroacademia.fandom.com/wiki/Eijiro_Kirishima\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Red Riot</a> during the <a href=\"https://myheroacademia.fandom.com/wiki/Shie_Hassaikai_Arc\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Shie Hassaikai Arc</a> and <a href=\"https://myheroacademia.fandom.com/wiki/Endeavor_Agency_Arc\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Endeavor Agency Arc</a> with the addition of <a href=\"https://myheroacademia.fand